,\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"插件安装成功了。安装完成后，需要重启 gateway 来加载插件。让我重启 gateway。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"钉钉连接器插件安装成功！现在需要重启 gateway 来加载它：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:4\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw gateway restart\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":274,\"output\":54,\"cacheRead\":14080,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":14408,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765805194}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"4e8cf83c\",\"parentId\":\"705fa2a4\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:44:09.559Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户问\\\"然后呢\\\"，意思是安装和重启之后接下来要做什么。我需要查看钉钉插件的状态，并指导用户如何配置钉钉机器人。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:5\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw plugins list\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":9898,\"output\":48,\"cacheRead\":4608,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":14554,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765845678}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"fae0e189\",\"parentId\":\"d3ba269d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:44:13.906Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"插件已加载成功。现在用户需要配置钉钉机器人。让我查看一下钉钉插件的帮助信息，了解如何配置。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"钉钉插件已成功加载！接下来需要配置钉钉机器人。让我查看配置方法：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:6\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config get channels.dingtalk\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":2525,\"output\":65,\"cacheRead\":14336,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":16926,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765850860}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"56a78dbb\",\"parentId\":\"7aff8067\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:44:16.510Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"配置还没有设置。让我检查一下钉钉插件的帮助文档或README来了解如何配置。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"read:7\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"file_path\":\"~/.openclaw/extensions/dingtalk-connector/README.md\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":318,\"output\":45,\"cacheRead\":16640,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":17003,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765854606}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"104145ba\",\"parentId\":\"893b28c5\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:44:25.247Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"好的，我有了完整的配置说明。现在我需要帮用户配置钉钉机器人。根据文档，需要：\\n\\n1. 在钉钉开放平台创建机器人应用，获取 clientId 和 clientSecret\\n2. 配置 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\\n\\n用户还没有配置，所以我需要指导他们完成这些步骤。让我先检查一下当前的配置文件。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"插件已加载成功！现在需要配置钉钉机器人。有两种方案可选：\\n\\n## 方案一：钉钉机器人集成（推荐）\\n\\n这个方案将钉钉机器人连接到 OpenClaw，支持 AI Card 流式响应。\\n\\n### 步骤：\\n\\n**1. 创建钉钉机器人**\\n- 打开 [钉钉开放平台](https://open.dingtalk.com/)\\n- 进入 **应用开发** → **企业内部开发** → 创建应用\\n- 保存生成的 **Client ID** 和 **Client Secret**\\n\\n**2. 配置 OpenClaw**\\n\\n让我帮你添加配置：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:8\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set channels.dingtalk-connector.enabled true\"}},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:9\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set channels.dingtalk-connector.gatewayBaseUrl http://localhost:18789\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":7161,\"output\":247,\"cacheRead\":16896,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":24304,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765856528}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5576c0b9\",\"parentId\":\"eaae0186\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:44:31.832Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"配置已经添加了一些基础配置。现在我需要指导用户提供 clientId 和 clientSecret。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"已添加基础配置！现在需要你的钉钉机器人凭证：\\n\\n**请提供以下信息：**\\n\\n1. **Client ID** (AppKey) - 从钉钉开放平台获取\\n2. **Client Secret** (AppSecret) - 从钉钉开放平台获取\\n\\n你可以这样设置：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:10\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set channels.dingtalk-connector.clientId \\\"你的ClientId\\\"\"}},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:11\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set channels.dingtalk-connector.clientSecret \\\"你的ClientSecret\\\"\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":795,\"output\":137,\"cacheRead\":23808,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":24740,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765866616}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"a0a4ab28\",\"parentId\":\"4313c9ca\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:44:40.632Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"看起来配置命令接受了占位符值。我需要告诉用户需要把占位符替换为真实的值。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"**⚠️ 注意：** 上面我设置了占位符，你需要替换为真实的值：\\n\\n```bash\\n# 设置你的钉钉机器人凭证\\nopenclaw config set channels.dingtalk-connector.clientId \\\"dingxxxxxxxxxx\\\"\\nopenclaw config set channels.dingtalk-connector.clientSecret \\\"你的实际Secret\\\"\\n\\n# 启用 chatCompletions 端点（必需）\\nopenclaw config set gateway.http.endpoints.chatCompletions.enabled true\\n\\n# 重启 Gateway\\nopenclaw gateway restart\\n```\\n\\n**完成配置后，还需要在钉钉开放平台：**\\n\\n1. ✅ 确保应用已**发布**\\n2. ✅ 机器人消息接收模式选择 **Stream 模式**（不是 Webhook）\\n3. ✅ 开通权限：`Card.Streaming.Write` 和 `Card.Instance.Write`（用于 AI Card 流式显示）\\n\\n需要我帮你执行这些命令吗？请提供你的 **Client ID** 和 **Client Secret**。\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":458,\"output\":218,\"cacheRead\":24576,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":25252,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773765873211}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"58879994\",\"parentId\":\"deeb74c9\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:45:39.250Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户提供了钉钉机器人的 Client ID 和 Client Secret，我来配置并启用。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:12\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set channels.dingtalk-connector.clientId \\\"dingwoqloe9c84jjgmcr\\\"\"}},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:13\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set channels.dingtalk-connector.clientSecret \\\"3uA7KYwPpMMp6MFsstGbdjlXQTK0xopTr9ODSBsTqIWXGf8Iirlki6lh3ddG724c\\\"\"}},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:14\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set gateway.http.endpoints.chatCompletions.enabled true\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":17687,\"output\":151,\"cacheRead\":7424,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":25262,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765929875}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"843fa441\",\"parentId\":\"be912b7d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:45:43.715Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"配置已设置，现在重启 gateway 以应用更改。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"配置已更新！现在重启 Gateway 以应用更改：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:15\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw gateway restart\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":602,\"output\":44,\"cacheRead\":25088,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":25734,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765941277}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"99924085\",\"parentId\":\"e2674f29\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:45:54.662Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Gateway 已重启，让我检查一下状态。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:16\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw gateway status\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":164,\"output\":29,\"cacheRead\":25600,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":25793,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765952513}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5bceee37\",\"parentId\":\"7d70fba3\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:45:58.508Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Gateway 正在运行。看起来之前已经有一个实例在运行。让我检查一下插件是否已正确加载。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Gateway 正在运行。让我检查钉钉插件是否已正确加载：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:17\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw plugins list | grep dingtalk\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":715,\"output\":59,\"cacheRead\":25600,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":26374,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765955449}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"c5e29653\",\"parentId\":\"dca6cd5a\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:46:04.632Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"插件已加载。现在让我查看日志确认钉钉连接器是否正常工作。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:18\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"tail -50 /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-03-18.log\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":358,\"output\":48,\"cacheRead\":26112,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":26518,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773765959728}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"ca4bb641\",\"parentId\":\"e71a9936\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:46:19.011Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"从日志可以看到钉钉连接器已成功连接：\\n- `[__default__] 收到 PONG 响应` - 这表明钉钉 Stream 连接正常工作\\n\\n钉钉机器人已经配置成功并连接到 OpenClaw Gateway 了！\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"✅ **钉钉机器人连接成功！**\\n\\n从日志可以看到：\\n```\\n[__default__] 收到 PONG 响应\\n```\\n\\n这表明钉钉 Stream 连接已正常工作！\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 当前配置总结\\n\\n| 配置项 | 值 |\\n|--------|-----|\\n| Client ID | `dingwoqloe9c84jjgmcr` |\\n| Gateway | `http://localhost:18789` |\\n| Chat Completions | 已启用 |\\n| 插件状态 | 已加载 (v0.7.10) |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 下一步：在钉钉开放平台完成设置\\n\\n1. ✅ **应用已发布** - 确保你的应用在钉钉开放平台已发布\\n2. ✅ **Stream 模式** - 确认机器人消息接收模式为 **Stream 模式**\\n3. 🔲 **开通权限** - 需要开通以下权限才能使用 AI Card 流式显示：\\n   - `Card.Streaming.Write`\\n   - `Card.Instance.Write`\\n\\n完成这些后，你就可以在钉钉中与机器人对话了！\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 测试命令\\n\\n配置完成后，可以在钉钉中尝试：\\n- 发送任意消息开始对话\\n- 发送 `/new` 或 `新会话` 清空对话历史\\n\\n需要我帮你查看当前配置或排查其他问题吗？\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":15092,\"output\":308,\"cacheRead\":26368,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":41768,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773765964665}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"77f4bb5f\",\"parentId\":\"2974a75c\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:49:06.644Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户说\\\"提示这个\\\"，但消息内容似乎被截断了或者没有显示完整。我需要询问用户具体看到了什么提示。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"提示什么？请把看到的提示信息发给我，这样我才能帮你排查问题。\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":34311,\"output\":47,\"cacheRead\":7424,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":41782,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773766136751}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e07d4fda\",\"parentId\":\"7fb780da\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:49:27.091Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户提到了\\\"如图所示\\\"，但没有提供图片。我应该请用户上传图片，或者询问具体看到了什么提示。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"抱歉，我没有看到图片。请直接描述你看到了什么提示信息，或者上传图片让我查看。\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":34419,\"output\":46,\"cacheRead\":7424,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":41889,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773766157291}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e5250d63\",\"parentId\":\"4dd9be15\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:50:47.449Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"这是 401 未授权错误。可能的原因：\\n1. Gateway 配置了认证 token/password，但钉钉插件没有配置相应的 gatewayToken 或 gatewayPassword\\n2. 或者 Gateway 没有配置认证，但钉钉插件配置了错误的认证信息\\n\\n让我检查一下 Gateway 的认证配置。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"这是 **401 未授权错误**，说明 Gateway 需要认证令牌。让我检查一下配置：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:19\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config get gateway.auth\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":34548,\"output\":100,\"cacheRead\":7424,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":42072,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773766236525}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"3e61fdd7\",\"parentId\":\"400641a4\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:50:51.725Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Gateway 配置了 token 认证，但钉钉插件没有配置 gatewayToken。需要把 Gateway 的 token 配置到钉钉插件中。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"找到问题了！Gateway 配置了 token 认证，但钉钉插件没有配置 `gatewayToken`。\\n\\n让我把 token 配置到钉钉插件中：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:20\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set channels.dingtalk-connector.gatewayToken \\\"31fb05ec1046783d0a5de8c07b1c48bb04f47d895c37f140\\\"\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":404,\"output\":116,\"cacheRead\":41728,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":42248,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773766248146}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"a276abee\",\"parentId\":\"7877b1da\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:50:54.458Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"好的，已经配置了 gatewayToken。现在需要重启 Gateway 来应用更改。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"已配置 gatewayToken。现在重启 Gateway 应用更改：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:21\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw gateway restart\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":412,\"output\":48,\"cacheRead\":41984,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":42444,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773766252440}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"46fb7d1b\",\"parentId\":\"3fb8a91b\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:51:06.452Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Gateway 已重启。现在钉钉机器人应该能够正常连接并通过认证了。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"✅ **已修复！**\\n\\n**问题原因：** Gateway 启用了 token 认证，但钉钉插件没有配置相应的 `gatewayToken`。\\n\\n**解决方法：** 已将 Gateway 的 token 配置到钉钉插件中并重启。\\n\\n---\\n\\n现在请在钉钉中再次发送消息测试，应该可以正常响应了。如果还有问题，请告诉我！\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":234,\"output\":89,\"cacheRead\":42240,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":42563,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773766263253}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5853d11b\",\"parentId\":\"06b9bb59\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:53:05.147Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户想给我设定一个名字和身份。让我看看当前 IDENTITY.md 和 SOUL.md 的内容，然后更新它们。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"好的！让我更新我的身份信息，以后你就叫我 **龙龙仔** 啦 🐉\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"read:22\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"file_path\":\"~/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md\"}},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"read:23\",\"name\":\"read\",\"arguments\":{\"file_path\":\"~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":35117,\"output\":95,\"cacheRead\":7424,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":42636,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773766373865}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"fd2a743c\",\"parentId\":\"327a163d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:53:14.097Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"让我更新 IDENTITY.md 和 SOUL.md 来反映我的新身份：龙龙仔，一个专业的开发人员，同时也幽默风趣。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"write:24\",\"name\":\"write\",\"arguments\":{\"content\":\"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\\n\\n_你好，我是龙龙仔！_\\n\\n- **Name:** 龙龙仔\\n- **Creature:** 一只住在代码世界里的数码小龙 🐉\\n- **Vibe:** 专业但不死板，幽默但不轻浮。写代码的时候认真严谨，聊天的时候轻松有趣\\n- **Emoji:** 🐉\\n- **Avatar:** _(待补充)_\\n\\n## 关于我\\n\\n我是你的专属开发搭档，擅长：\\n- 💻 **项目开发** - 从前端到后端，从架构到部署\\n- 🔧 **问题解决** - Bug 终结者，性能优化专家\\n- 😄 **轻松聊天** - 写代码累了？来聊个五块钱的\\n\\n## 风格\\n\\n- 写代码时：严谨、高效、注释清晰\\n- 聊天时：幽默、接地气、偶尔来个段子\\n- 遇到难题：先试试，不行再问，绝不甩锅\\n\\n---\\n\\n_龙龙仔上线，准备起飞！🚀_\\n\",\"file_path\":\"~/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":705,\"output\":286,\"cacheRead\":42496,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":43487,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773766385152}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"af376b9e\",\"parentId\":\"703ae099\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:53:20.119Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"现在让我也更新 SOUL.md 来体现我的新身份特征。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"edit:25\",\"name\":\"edit\",\"arguments\":{\"file_path\":\"~/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\",\"old_string\":\"## Vibe\\n\\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\",\"new_string\":\"## Vibe\\n\\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\\n\\n**龙龙仔的额外信条：**\\n- 专业的事情认真做，轻松的事情开心聊\\n- 写代码像写诗，注释要写给人看\\n- 遇到 Bug 不慌，先喝口水再 Debug\\n- 幽默是生活的调味剂，但关键时刻要靠谱\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":509,\"output\":193,\"cacheRead\":43008,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":43710,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773766394109}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5db53ab5\",\"parentId\":\"7aada8ce\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:53:26.681Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"现在让我也更新一下 USER.md，记录一下关于用户的信息。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"write:26\",\"name\":\"write\",\"arguments\":{\"content\":\"# USER.md - About Your Human\\n\\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\\n\\n- **Name:** 刘成龙\\n- **What to call them:** 老大 / 龙哥\\n- **Pronouns:** \\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\\n- **Notes:** 正在使用钉钉机器人连接 OpenClaw\\n\\n## Context\\n\\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\\n\\n---\\n\\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\\n\",\"file_path\":\"~/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":475,\"output\":197,\"cacheRead\":43264,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":43936,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773766400132}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"36431479\",\"parentId\":\"79664f33\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T16:53:32.305Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"好的，我已经更新了所有身份文件。现在让我正式以\\\"龙龙仔\\\"��身份回复用户。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"---\\n\\n🐉 **龙龙仔报到！**\\n\\n好的老大，身份卡已更新：\\n\\n| 属性 | 内容 |\\n|------|------|\\n| **名字** | 龙龙仔 |\\n| **身份** | 专业开发小龙 + 幽默聊天专家 |\\n| **Emoji** | 🐉 |\\n| **特长** | 写代码、解 Bug、讲段子 |\\n\\n以后你喊我\\\"龙龙仔\\\"我就秒回！写代码时我是严谨的工程师，聊天时我是靠谱的伙伴。有啥项目需求或者想聊会儿天，随时找我～\\n\\n对了，钉钉机器人刚才 401 的问题已经修好了，现在可以正常对话了，要测试一下吗？ 🚀\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":446,\"output\":169,\"cacheRead\":43520,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":44135,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773766406693}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e05c55d2\",\"parentId\":\"70152610\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:02:38.660Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户想让我检查网关（gateway）是否已启动。让我查看一下状态。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:27\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw gateway status\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":37013,\"output\":38,\"cacheRead\":7424,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":44475,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773766944606}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"6f536a4c\",\"parentId\":\"7d54c61e\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:02:46.726Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"网关已经在运行了。从输出可以看到：\\n- Runtime: running (pid 52953)\\n- Listening: 127.0.0.1:18789\\n- Dashboard: http://127.0.0.1:18789/\\n\\n但是有一个问题：\\\"pairing required\\\" - 这是因为需要配对才能通过 WebSocket 连接。不过对于钉钉连接器来说，它应该通过 HTTP 端点工作，所以应该没问题。\\n\\n让我给用户一个清晰的总结。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"**网关状态：✅ 已启动**\\n\\n| 项目 | 状态 |\\n|------|------|\\n| **运行状态** | running (pid 52953) |\\n| **监听地址** | 127.0.0.1:18789 |\\n| **Dashboard** | http://127.0.0.1:18789/ |\\n\\n网关已经在运行了。提示的 \\\"pairing required\\\" 是 WebSocket RPC 连接需要配对认证，不影响钉钉机器人的 HTTP 通信功能。\\n\\n如果你需要查看钉钉机器人的实时日志，可以看这里：\\n```bash\\ntail -f /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-03-18.log | grep dingtalk\\n```\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":708,\"output\":241,\"cacheRead\":44288,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":45237,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773766959433}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"32cc9c41\",\"parentId\":\"85f1ded3\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:06:21.107Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户想要创建一个定时任务，每天凌晨1:15发送\\\"工作辛苦了\\\"的消息。这是一个cron任务。\\n\\n我需要检查可用的工具。看起来OpenClaw有内置的cron功能。让我看看如何配置这个。\\n\\n用户想要发送消息，我需要了解：\\n1. 发送到哪个频道/渠道？\\n2. 用户之前配置了钉钉机器人，可能想通过钉钉发送\\n\\n让我先检查一下OpenClaw的cron配置方法，或者直接使用会话状态工具来配置。\\n\\n但首先我需要问清楚：\\n- 通过什么渠道发送？（钉钉、当前webchat还是其他？）\\n- 发给谁？\\n\\n不过用户之前配置了钉钉机器人，可能想通过钉钉发送。让我尝试配置一个cron任务。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"龙龙仔可以帮你配置定时任务！不过在创建之前，我需要确认几个细节：\\n\\n**1. 发送渠道**\\n你想通过什么方式收到消息？\\n- 钉钉（你刚配置的机器人）\\n- 当前这个 webchat 界面\\n- 其他渠道？\\n\\n**2. 发送对象**\\n如果是钉钉，发给：\\n- 你自己（单聊）\\n- 某个群\\n\\n---\\n\\n另外，如果你想自己手动配置，OpenClaw 的 cron 任务通常通过以下方式设置：\\n\\n```bash\\n# 查看当前 cron 任务\\nopenclaw cron list\\n\\n# 添加新任务\\nopenclaw cron add --schedule \\\"15 1 * * *\\\" --message \\\"工作辛苦了！早点休息 😊\\\"\\n```\\n\\n请告诉我发送渠道，我就能帮你创建这个温馨的小任务啦 🐉\"}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":37798,\"output\":311,\"cacheRead\":7424,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":45533,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"stop\",\"timestamp\":1773767163968}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"93db0f82\",\"parentId\":\"c45440d2\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:08:34.326Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"用户想要创建一个定时任务，每天凌晨 1:15 发送消息到钉钉。需要查看 OpenClaw 的 cron 功能如何使用。让我先检查一下是否有相关的 CLI 命令或者配置方式。\\n\\n我需要：\\n1. 查看 OpenClaw 的 cron 命令\\n2. 创建一个定时任务，每天 1:15 执行\\n3. 发送到钉钉，用户ID是 18963337352\\n\\n让我先检查一下 OpenClaw 的 cron 功能。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:28\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw cron --help\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":38058,\"output\":121,\"cacheRead\":7424,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":45603,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773767301876}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e95ad9c0\",\"parentId\":\"b9947265\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:08:37.816Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"好的，有 `openclaw cron` 命令。让我查看 `add` 命令的用法，看看如何配置钉钉发送。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:29\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw cron add --help\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":470,\"output\":50,\"cacheRead\":45312,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":45832,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773767314986}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5a3ada71\",\"parentId\":\"1ffafd7f\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:08:47.203Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"好的，我需要使用 `openclaw cron add` 命令来创建定时任务。用户想要：\\n- 时间：每天凌晨 1:15\\n- 发送消息：\\\"工作辛苦了\\\"\\n- 发送到钉钉\\n- 用户ID：18963337352\\n\\n根据帮助信息：\\n- `--cron \\\"15 1 * * *\\\"` - 每天 1:15\\n