7.0.0.1:18789\\n2. Gateway 配置了 token 认证模式，token 是 `31fb05ec1046783d0a5de8c07b1c48bb04f47d895c37f140`\\n3. CLI 连接 Gateway 时出现 \\\"pairing required\\\" 错误\\n\\n\\\"pairing required\\\" 意味着 CLI 需要通过某种配对流程来认证。这可能是因为：\\n1. CLI 需要使用不同的认证方式\\n2. 需要先在 Gateway Dashboard 中进行配对\\n3. 需要使用特定的命令来配对\\n\\n让我检查一下配对相关的命令或配置。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"**Gateway Token:** `31fb05ec1046783d0a5de8c07b1c48bb04f47d895c37f140`\\n\\n\\\"Pairing required\\\" 是因为 Gateway 启用了 token 认证，但 CLI 默认尝试用 WebSocket RPC 连接，需要额外的配对步骤。\\n\\n让我帮你检查如何配对：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:51\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw pair --help 2>/dev/null || openclaw auth --help 2>/dev/null || openclaw gateway pair --help 2>/dev/null\"}},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:52\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config get gateway.remote\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":45413,\"output\":300,\"cacheRead\":7424,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":53137,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773767501220}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"13f5dfc0\",\"parentId\":\"971e906b\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:12:06.372Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"我看到了 `pairing` 命令。让我查看它的帮助信息。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:53\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw pairing --help\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":1407,\"output\":35,\"cacheRead\":52736,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":54178,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773767522625}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"a7745af6\",\"parentId\":\"8d26e1f9\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:12:11.950Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"让我看看配对相关的文档。OpenClaw 的配对机制似乎是为了安全 DM 配对。但 Gateway 的 \\\"pairing required\\\" 可能是不同的概念。\\n\\n让我查看一下 Gateway 的配对或认证方式。可能需要配置 `gateway.remote.url` 或 `gateway.remote.token`。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"web_fetch:54\",\"name\":\"web_fetch\",\"arguments\":{\"url\":\"https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/pairing\",\"maxChars\":2000}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":346,\"output\":93,\"cacheRead\":54016,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":54455,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773767527516}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e5a377b2\",\"parentId\":\"64fc0232\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:12:15.464Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"这是关于节点配对的文档，不是 CLI 到 Gateway 的配对问题。\\n\\n让我看看 CLI 如何连接到 Gateway。可能需要设置 `gateway.remote.url` 和 `gateway.remote.token`。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"让我检查 CLI 如何连接到 Gateway：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:55\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config get gateway\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":850,\"output\":68,\"cacheRead\":54272,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":55190,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773767532554}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"372253e9\",\"parentId\":\"9906852d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:12:19.806Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Gateway 配置看起来正常。让我尝试配置 `gateway.remote` 来让 CLI 能够连接到 Gateway。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:56\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set gateway.remote.url \\\"ws://127.0.0.1:18789\\\"\"}},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:57\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw config set gateway.remote.token \\\"31fb05ec1046783d0a5de8c07b1c48bb04f47d895c37f140\\\"\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":340,\"output\":109,\"cacheRead\":55040,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":55489,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773767536164}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"664c52aa\",\"parentId\":\"a04b03df\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-17T17:12:25.718Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"好的，我配置了 `gateway.remote.url` 和 `gateway.remote.token`。现在让我重启 Gateway 并测试连接。\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"reasoning_content\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"现在重启 Gateway 并测试连接：\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"exec:58\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"openclaw gateway restart\"}}],\"api\":\"openai-completions\",\"provider\":\"moonshot\",\"model\":\"kimi-k2.5\",\"usage\":{\"input\":473,\"output\":53,\"cacheRead\":55296,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":55822,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1773767541195}}","cwd":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773845230771}}
{"type":"message","id":"78671880","parentId":"b4588f38","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:47:43.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从日志来看，我发现问题了！从会话历史记录可以看到：\n\n1. 有一个会话 (`920b20e4-600c-4a38-b815-e22359e15985.jsonl`) 有 **408 行**，**1.2MB** 大小\n2. 这个会话是昨天（3月17日）安装钉钉插件时产生的，持续了很多轮对话\n3. 多个 token 使用记录显示消耗了大量 token（有些请求超过 20k-40k token）\n\n更重要的是，在日志中我看到了 **429 余额不足错误**：\n```\n\"errorMessage\":\"429 Your account org-6043a8fa6e38435cbbe4f39b0124b83f <ak-f8erfeu41r4i11auwjz1> is suspended due to insufficient balance, please recharge your account or check your plan and billing details\"\n```\n\n这表明 Moonshot API 账户余额不足被暂停了。\n\n让我总结今天的情况并给用户一个清晰的答案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我查看了今天的日志和会话历史，发现问题的关键了！\n\n## 🔍 问题分析\n\n### 1. **会话历史累积**\n昨天（3月17日）安装钉钉插件时产生了一个 **1.2MB** 的会话历史文件（408行），包含大量的工具调用和输出。\n\n### 2. **Token 消耗热点**\n从日志中可以看到多个高 token 消耗的请求：\n- `totalTokens: 36188` - 查询会话历史\n- `totalTokens: 41768` - 钉钉配置回复\n- `totalTokens: 45237` - Gateway 状态检查\n\n### 3. **API 账户余额不足** ⚠️\n**重要发现**：日志中多次出现 429 错误：\n```\nYour account is suspended due to insufficient balance\n```\n你的 Moonshot API 账户余额不足已被暂停！\n\n---\n\n## 🛡️ 如何避免未来大量 Token 消耗\n\n### 1. **会话上下文清理**\n```bash\n# 定期清理旧会话历史\nopenclaw sessions clean\n\n# 或者手动删除大文件\nls -la ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n```\n\n### 2. **使用 Isolated 会话**\n对于复杂任务，使用独立会话，不累积到主会话：\n```bash\nopenclaw sessions spawn --isolated \"你的任务\"\n```\n\n### 3. **限制上下文长度**\n在 `openclaw.json` 配置中设置最大上下文：\n```json\n{\n  \"models\": {\n    \"contextWindow\": 100000  // 限制上下文长度\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 4. **监控 Token 使用**\n```bash\nopenclaw status  # 查看当前 token 使用情况\n```\n\n### 5. **为 Cron 任务使用轻量级模型**\n如果 cron 任务不需要复杂推理，可以指定更便宜的模型。\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 当前需要先处理的问题\n\n**你的 Moonshot API 账户余额不足**，需要：\n1. 充值 Moonshot API 账户\n2. 或者更换其他可用的 API Key\n\n需要我帮你切换到其他模型提供商吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":54474,"output":656,"cacheRead":36096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91226,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773845230776}}
